edu.udel.cis.vsl.sarl.expr.common

Class CommonNumericExpressionFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.udel.cis.vsl.sarl.expr.common.CommonNumericExpressionFactory
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    NumericExpressionFactory

    public class CommonNumericExpressionFactory
extends java.lang.Object
implements NumericExpressionFactory
    Given a numeric factory that deals with expressions of ideal type, and a numeric factory that deals with expressions of herbrand type, this factory puts them together to work on any numeric type.
